fields.message: Hey! I saw your message about Wicked, and I wondered if you could tell me some more about the show?
Hey! Where can I find the cast list for this musical?
Hey! Where can I see this information?
Look on the theatre's website, it usually says there :)
What shows have you seen recently?
Do they speak any Italian in the show?
I'm not actually sure... I'm sure that any Italian will have fairly obvious meanings anyway! They want everyone to be able to enjoy the show :)
What, like in Encanto? Where it's a bit obvious what they are meaning with the Spanish that they use?
All you have to do is Google - usually their websites have a list :)
Do you think it would matter if I didn't take a coat to Frozen? Although, to be fair, at the moment I do live in Hadestown which is very hot! I might find it hard to adjust.
